# Patch 001: Force LLVM/LLD backend on Darwin 26+
#
# Target: src/Compilation.zig or src/link/MachO.zig
#
# When host OS is macOS 26+, default to LLVM/LLD backend instead of
# self-hosted Mach-O linker, which has __CONST_ZIG segment ordering
# issues on Tahoe (upstream issue #25521).
#
# This patch will be generated from the actual Zig source once
# .cel/.src/ is populated by running: ./cel/build.sh --patch-only
